{"tid":873520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社萬歲】英國檔案解密行程目標達成！","createTime":"2018-10-23T13:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T08:47:12.000Z","uid":138409,"like":116,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7288b23afec6232e683efb41467a2b4fd97205","tid":873520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"偶爾都係會有好消息嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得最好好似哈佛大學嘅nuremberg trials project咁<br />\n<a href=\"http://nuremberg.law.harvard.edu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuremberg.law.harvard.edu%2F&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f5b39a12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nuremberg.law.harvard.edu/</a><br />\n整個電子圖書館<br />\n一search就找到想要嘅檔案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kimching.geographer/posts/10155979567741247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkimching.geographer%2Fposts%2F10155979567741247&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3a756274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kimching.geographer/posts/10155979567741247</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RD3cXQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRD3cXQZ.jpg&h=4f62289f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次解密香港檔案的旅程即將完結，總結這兩星期的行程成果：<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">我們已成功數碼化過300份香港解密歷史檔案</span>，包括香港前途、政制改革、基建發展、重要人物等議題；<br />\n<br />\n2. 建立約有50人的倫敦檔案工作小組社群，現場提供整理檔案工作教學，持續英國國家檔案館的檔案挖掘工作；<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">共獲130位熱心朋友支持，為5位研究員籌得近9成是次倫敦行程基本費用</span>；<br />\n<br />\n4. 為封存過久 (上50年) 的重要香港歷史檔案申請上訴，爭取盡早解封及封閉理由。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終於可以有信心向大家宣佈，香港前途研究計劃 Decoding Hong Kong's History 兩年來已整理到過1,000份歷史解密檔案，對認識及研究香港政改及民主化歷史、基本法原意、都市發展等問題有莫大意義。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n如無意外，這將會是至今香港最整全的80-90年代香港解密檔案文庫，成為研究該段時期的香港體制發展，與及保存香港歷史憶記的重要根據。<br />\n<br />\n下一步，我們就會著手公開相關歷史檔案的工作，希望讓社會公眾、研究者盡快可以有渠道使用到這次檔案；另外亦會策劃一系列的專題文章及傳媒報導，相信大家很快就會陸續看到，這批檔案對於當今各種香港重大問題的歷史意義。<br />\n<br />\n這次旅程完結，在此代表研究團隊感謝各位參與者與支持者，仍希望大家可以繼續小額支持我們的檔案工作，收得新捐款將會全數用於支持倫敦港人義工到檔案館的交通費、籌建公開檔案文庫及檔案研究工作。<br />\n<br />\n💪自訂金額支持：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IVW56L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IVW56L&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f2f52756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IVW56L</a><br />\n<br />\n✍️銀行轉帳支持：<br />\n收款銀行：匯豐銀行 HSBC <br />\n銀行編號：004<br />\n收款戶口：640-198305-001<br />\n戶口名稱：Liber Research Community (HK) Company Limited"},{"pid":"57d3cf07f07b2aca4bdafd8bbf1d8308a45316ed","tid":873520,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"加油！<br />\n<br />\n希望你地一切順利！"},{"pid":"12d5c65fdc03863fc8b1f86881aa2a68a7e981aa","tid":873520,"uid":73613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1323d2bbcd5c6fa90fe05f6cba5f71a05e45d16","tid":873520,"uid":19005,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"有冇轉數快戶口？ 唔方便用paypal"},{"pid":"0d5b47bca6fbd300763cd34326df048c8ef5a61c","tid":873520,"uid":102421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"要唔要IT support?"},{"pid":"8f27c7cd182b0cab1d7d61c627cf4cf2b120c0fe","tid":873520,"uid":61105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"捐左少少支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b88e2700fcee1bb686b9254635fa732e617bf1","tid":873520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1323d2bbcd5c6fa90fe05f6cba5f71a05e45d16","tid":873520,"uid":19005,"lik