7:41.000Z","msg":"要唔要IT support?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"我記得佢地之前好似搞緊OCR<br />\n將檔案電子化<br />\n巴打不妨主動聯絡佢地<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2F&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9b9beb4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/</a><br />\n佢地好nice<br />\n一向都好歡迎公眾群策群力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08eded93f81da9a7de87618ba473a3f2a372c1c","tid":873520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d221f905b680833e16815ef74e0fa6f610df728","tid":873520,"uid":98493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"想問下數碼化係做咗OCR 未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"係呢個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地之前應該搞緊<br />\n不過似乎幾慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/977221792431784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F977221792431784&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7dc04e95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/977221792431784</a><br />\n<br />\n夜闌人靜之下，我地部超級（慢）電腦以「秒速0.02毫米」速度做緊檔案OCR。呢個畫面，係咪好high tech呢（#IT高手饒命唔好笑9me）？<br />\n<br />\n我地辛苦挖掘返來嘅解密檔案，其實同而家政府部門嘅文件一樣都係原始嘅圖片格式，search唔到入面嘅keyword。但今時今日做研究，點可以好似政府咁懶咁low-tech？<br />\n<br />\n我地得到IT高人嘅指點，教我地OCR（Optical Character Recognition），中文叫「光學字元識別」，即係數碼化d解密檔案。咁樣檔案就可以search到，大大加快研究嘅進程。呢個過程需要大量嘅人力同電力，我地幾部電腦已開行turbo，好似掘Bitcoin咁土炮咁做咗幾個月。暫時已經有300份檔案已搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日做研究，IT技術真係不可或缺（#再次向IT人才致敬 ）。<br />\n<br />\n#政府做可能又要幾百萬<br />\n#比佢做不如比我哋做啦<br />\n#政府d文件冇做OCR人憎鬼厭<br />\n#土炮"},{"pid":"5cb46bb7ea66525c78254cb7ae916a40adbdf8e1","tid":873520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5b47bca6fbd300763cd34326df048c8ef5a61c","tid":873520,"uid":102421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"要唔要IT support?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"應該要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打對OCR方面有無研究？<br />\n我覺得佢地應該幾需要呢方面嘅技術支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/977221792431784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdecodinghkhistory%2Fposts%2F977221792431784&d=tpHHwekCy3Jj1mQC8gBk9W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7dc04e95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/decodinghkhistory/posts/977221792431784</a><br />\n夜闌人靜之下，我地部超級（慢）電腦以「秒速0.02毫米」速度做緊檔案OCR。呢個畫面，係咪好high tech呢（#IT高手饒命唔好笑9me）？<br />\n<br />\n我地辛苦挖掘返來嘅解密檔案，其實同而家政府部門嘅文件一樣都係原始嘅圖片格式，search唔到入面嘅keyword。但今時今日做研究，點可以好似政府咁懶咁low-tech？<br />\n<br />\n我地得到IT高人嘅指點，教我地OCR（Optical Character Recognition），中文叫「光學字元識別」，即係數碼化d解密檔案。咁樣檔案就可以search到，大大加快研究嘅進程。呢個過程需要大量嘅人力同電力，我地幾部電腦已開行turbo，好似掘Bitcoin咁土炮咁做咗幾個月。暫時已經有300份檔案已搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日做研究，IT技術真係不可或缺（#再次向IT人才致敬 ）。<br />\n<br />\n#政府做可能又要幾百萬<br />\n#比佢做不如比我哋做啦<br />\n#政府d文件冇做OCR人憎鬼厭<br />\n#土炮"},{"pid":"f6b783bc0cd91edc46e8ebcc8ab369b2329ec733","tid":873520,"uid":98795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"5b1294c1a842a516eb82ee7b911c6f9be1c163ea","tid":873520,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5cb46bb7ea66525c78254cb7ae916a40adbdf8e1","tid":873520,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5b47bca6fbd300763cd34326df048c8ef5a61c","tid":873520,"uid":102421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"